			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Chalkboard is a fast-growing local mobile ad network helping retailers to steer more walk-in traffic. A retail marketer can communicate promotions, today&rsquo;s specials, new product launches and much more all through the mobile phone and other such devices. Importantly this is made for SME market, where typically they cannot afford traditional marketing channels. Since our launch in February this year, more than 150 retailers have leveraged with us. More information can be found on our website: <a href="http://www.yourchalkboard.com">www.yourchalkboard.com</a></p>
<p>
	We are an extremely hyper-scaling start-up backed by US-based venture capital. We are looking for the following individuals who aspire to be part of a team with a distinct &quot;red-bulled&quot; company culture: CREATIVE + BARRIER-BREAKING + INTENSELY FUN! The individual we are looking for is someone who are passionate about the benefits of mobile technology, loves to interact with people and are not afraid, in fact loves to present to hundreds if not thousands of people. It helps too if you are self-motivated and can work independently and always strive to improve yourself.</p>
<p>
	If you have what it takes to be part of the fast-growing universe that is Chalkboard, drop us your resume and we&#39;ll get back to you!</p>
<p>
	<strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br />
	1. Locate, contact, inform and engage potential customers on ways that Chalkboard can help them increase customer traffic and improved profitability.<br />
	2. Maintain assigned accounts while developing new accounts inclusive of all the correspondence and paperwork related to these accounts.<br />
	3. Follow-up on customer issues and payment collection.<br />
	4. Perform effectively in a fast-paced small team environment.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Apply if you have:</strong><br />
	1. Proven outside sales experience (2 years minimum)<br />
	2. Strong prospecting, presentation, communication and closing skills<br />
	3. Able to work in fast-paced, self-directed entrepreneurial environment.<br />
	4. Exceptional verbal and written communication skills.<br />
	5. Highly proficient computer skills.<br />
	6. A self-starter with high self-motivation.<br />
	7. Preferably Singaporean citizen or PR.</p>
